{"lemma":"غَدِيرٌ","slug":"غَدِيرٌ","root":"غ.د.ر","root_slug":"غ-د-ر","root_link":"/words/roots/غ-د-ر","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":2},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n31502"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%BA%D9%8E%D8%AF%D9%90%D9%8A%D8%B1%D9%8C"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"pool"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"stream, creek"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/ɣa.diːr/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n31502","headword_ar":"غَدِيرٌ","root":"gdr","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A pool of water left by a torrent:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A 'Obeyd, S, M, K:) of the measure"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faEiylN","text_ar":"فَعِيلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"in the sense of the measure"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mufaAEilN","text_ar":"مُفَاعِلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gaAdarhu","text_ar":"غَادَرهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mufoEalN","text_ar":"مُفْعَلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^agodarahu","text_ar":"اَغْدَرَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; or, as some say, of the measure"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faEiylN","text_ar":"فَعِيلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"in the sense of the measure"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faAEilN","text_ar":"فَاعِلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S;) because it is unfaithful to those who come to it to water, failing when much wanted: (S, * TA:) but it is a subst.; [not an epithet; or an epithet in which the quality of a subst. predominates, and only used as a subst.:] you do not say"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"h`*aA maA='N gadiyrN","text_ar":"هٰذَا مَا=ءٌ غَدِيرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Lh:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a place in which rain-water stagnates,"},{"kind":"text","text":"whether"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"small"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"large, not remaining until the summer:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lth:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a river:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb:) [but this is extr.:] pl. [of pauc."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^agodirapN","text_ar":"اَغْدِرَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (occurring in a verse cited voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_il~aA","text_ar":"اـِلَّا"},{"kind":"text","text":", &c.,) and of mult.]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gudoraAnN","text_ar":"غُدْرَانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb, K, TA) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gudurN","text_ar":"غُدُرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Nh, L, TA,) which last is sometimes contracted into"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gudorN","text_ar":"غُدْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA:) in the K, the last pl. is said to be of the measure of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SuradN","text_ar":"صُرَدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; [i. e. ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gudarN","text_ar":"غُدَرٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":";] but this is inconsistent with what is said in other lexicons, as shown above: and it is also said in the K that"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gudarN","text_ar":"غُدَرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies the same as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gadiyrN","text_ar":"غَدِيرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in the sense first given above; but it appears that this is a pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gudorapN","text_ar":"غُدْرَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and that, in the K, we should read, for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waAlgadiyru, kaAlgadiyri","text_ar":"وَالغَدِيرُ, كَالغَدِيرِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and place this before, instead of after, its explanation. (TA.) ―         -b2-  Hence, (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A piece of herbage;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gadiyrapN","text_ar":"غَدِيرَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gudoraAnN","text_ar":"غُدْرَانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K, TA;) this is the only pl. (TA.) ―         -b3-  Hence also, (TA,) (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A sword;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA;) like as it is called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"luj~N","text_ar":"لُجٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) ―         -b4-  And ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gadiyrapN","text_ar":"غَدِيرَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"also signifies A she-camel"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"left by the pastor"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"behind the other camels;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and in like manner, a sheep, or goat. (S.)"}],"source_refs":["Lh","Lth","Msb","S","K","TA","Nh","L"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}